metadata.name: The Beginning of Greatness
metadata.description:
Be self-sufficient. Have a clear and developed sense of self. 

Be non-co-dependent, not prone to manipulation or control.
 
Solve your own problems. 

Don't be afraid of solitude, but don't be afraid of the company of people either. 

Don't overestimate, but don't underestimate your self-esteem either. 

Know and accept your own strengths and weaknesses. 

Know how to evaluate yourself, so you do not depend on other people's compliments and react calmly to criticism.
